# Use shadcn/ui as Component Library

Always prefer shadcn/ui components over building from scratch or using other UI libraries.

- Install components via `npx shadcn@latest add <component>`
- Import from `@/components/ui/<component>`
- Use Tailwind CSS for any custom styling on top of shadcn primitives
- Never use MUI, Chakra UI, Ant Design, or other UI libraries — shadcn/ui only

```tsx
// ❌ BAD — custom or third-party button
import { Button } from '@mui/material';

// ✅ GOOD — shadcn/ui button
import { Button } from '@/components/ui/button';
```
